### Campaigns API - Campanhas
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@contentType = application/json

### Tenant Authorization
@tenantId = tenant-abc123

### Campaign ID (será preenchido após criar uma campanha)
@campaignId =

###################
### CICLO DE VIDA COMPLETO
###################

### 1. Criar uma nova campanha
# @name createCampaign
POST {{baseUrl}}/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "campaign": {
    "name": "Campanha Q1 2026",
    "status": "not_started"
  }
}

### 2. Listar campanhas
GET {{baseUrl}}/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 3. Visualizar detalhes da campanha (substitua o ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/campaigns/{{campaignId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 4. Atualizar campanha
PUT {{baseUrl}}/campaigns/{{campaignId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "campaign": {
    "name": "Campanha Q1 2026 - Atualizada",
    "started_at": "2026-01-20T00:00:00.000000Z",
    "finished_at": "2026-03-31T23:59:59.999999Z"
  }
}

### 5. Iniciar campanha
POST {{baseUrl}}/campaigns/{{campaignId}}/start
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 6. Finalizar campanha
POST {{baseUrl}}/campaigns/{{campaignId}}/finish
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 7. Deletar campanha
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/campaigns/{{campaignId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###################
### TESTES DE VALIDAÇÃO
###################

